        "title": "Amazon is selling a 2-in-1 laptop and tablet for just $63",
        "content": "TheStreet aims to feature only the best products and services. If you buy something via one of our links, we may earn a commission. Why we love this deal If you rely on your tablet for work or simply for casual use and you're in need of an upgrade, Amazon offers plenty of options that will change the way you tackle daily computing tasks. From checking emails to streaming shows, they serve as portable devices that help you work and play. But if you want a tablet that also functions as a mini laptop, you're going to love our latest Amazon find. Originally priced at $73, the Coopers 2-in-1 Laptop and Tablet is now just $63, and it comes with everything you need in a tablet and more. Coopers 2-in-1 Laptop and Tablet, $63 (was $73) at Amazon Courtesy of Amazon Why do shoppers love it? This two-in-one laptop and tablet packs a punch for under $100. For starters, it runs Android 15, an incredibly user-friendly system with fast, secure performance. It features up to 8 gigabytes (GB) of RAM and 32 GB of ROM, with expandable memory up to 1 terabyte (TB), giving you more than enough space to store e-books, music, downloaded movies, and more. Related: Amazon is selling a 10-inch Android 13 tablet for just $52, and shoppers say it 'multitasks smoothly' With a 6000-milliampere-hour battery, you can get up to 13 hours on one charge, depending on your usage. That gives you more than enough time to watch a few movies and sort through emails before you have to recharge. It also has a 10.1-inch high-definition touchscreen that's big enough to be easy on the eyes while you use it. Plus, it has a 2-megapixel front camera and an 8-megapixel back camera to take photos, videos, and hop on a video call. As a two-in-one device, it's a level up from a standard tablet. It comes with an accessories bundle that includes a wireless keyboard, a wireless mouse, a protective case, a stylus pen, and a charging cable. Thanks to these extra accessories, you can easily switch from a standalone tablet to a mini laptop in a matter of seconds. What's more convenient than that? Details to know Memory: Up to 8 GB of RAM and 32 GB of ROM, expandable up to 1 TB. Operating system: Android 15. Battery life: Up to 13 hours. Screen size: 10.1 inches. Amazon shoppers love this two-in-one tablet and laptop, saying it's \"very fast\" and \"has a lot of memory.\" Many commented on its battery life, saying it's phenomenal. One reviewer claimed,\" The battery life on this is unreal. It will last like a week on one...",
